{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013b5Cqh5uDVj2UGazfzUrHe","type":"tool_result","content":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md:- No network isolation.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md:      network_allow = [\"docs.python.org\", \"internal.example.com\"]\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md:\tassert.Equal(t, \"docs.python.org,internal.example.com\", code.Config[\"container.network_allow\"])\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md:\t\t// String list (e.g., network_allow)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md:\tnetworkMode := \"none\"\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md:\t\t// TODO: Create custom network with allowlist. For now, use bridge.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md:\t\tnetworkMode = \"bridge\"\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md:\t\t\tNetworkMode: container.NetworkMode(networkMode),\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-04-step-timeout-design.md:container.* (image, network_allow, memory, agent_command, agent_args)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-system-design.md:      network_allow = [\"docs.python.org\", \"internal-docs.company.com\"]\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-system-design.md:2. **Network** — `--network none` by default. If `network_allow` is specified, Cloche creates\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-system-design.md:   a custom Docker network restricting egress to allowlisted domains via DNS proxy.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-system-design.md:- Container model: Docker, copy-in project files, git push for extraction, network allowlist","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01JL8mFVY8Rhg22KuPsWEiLJ","session_id":"6b861655-1988-46e5-92b9-f0a2db90f2de","uuid":"ad44967f-3a76-46e7-81e7-63ec97ea74ef"}
